def generate_pattern(K: int) -> list[str]:
    pattern = []
    l = list(range(2, K + 1))
    for _ in range(K):
        s = ''.join(map(str, l))
        pattern.append(s)
        x = l[0]
        l.pop(0)
        l.append(x)
    return pattern
